    This package provides buffered analyzers, which analyze the values after the benchmark
    de.linearbits.subframe.analyzer.stream
    This package provides analyzers, which compute the results incrementally based on incoming values
    de.linearbits.subframe.graph
    This package provides the main API for transforming and plotting the results of a benchmark
